snippet.title: Demonetisation: Nightmare of Black Money Doesn't Go Away from across the Country

localized.description:
Demonetisation: Nightmare of black money doesn't go away from across the country. Thousands of crores unaccounted money in denomination of Rs 2000, Rs 500 and Rs 1000 notes have been seized across the country. Income tax department, ED, CBI, Police and IB are keeping eyes on suspicious transactions and raiding accordingly.
